r 2018}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://mikethompson.house.gov/ Congressman Mike Thompson] official U.S. House site\n* [http://www.mikethompsonforcongress.com/ Campaign website]\n* {{Dmoz|Regional/North_America/United_States/California/Government/Federal/US_House_of_Representatives/Mike_Thompson_%5BD-05%5D|Mike Thompson}}\n* {{C-SPAN|mikethompson}}\n* {{CongLinks | congbio=T000460 | votesmart=3564 | fec=H8CA01109 | congress=mike-thompson/T000460}}<!--\nLinks formerly displayed via the CongLinks template:\n* [http://ballotpedia.org/Mike_Thompson_(California) Biography] at [[Ballotpedia]]\n* [http://www.nndb.com/people/756/000040636 Biography] at [[NNDB]]\n* [http://www.govtrack.us/congress/members/400403 Congressional profile] at [[GovTrack]]\n* [http://www.opencongress.org/people/show/400403 Congressional profile] at [[Participatory Politics Foundation|OpenCongress]]\n* [http://www.rollcall.com/members/28.html Congressional profile] at ''[[Roll Call]]''\n* [http://www.opensecrets.org/politicians/summary.php?cid=N00007419 Financial information (federal office)] at [[Center for Responsive Politics|OpenSecrets.org]]\n* [https://apps.washingtonpost.com/politics/capitol-assets/member/michael-thompson Financial investments (personal)] at ''[[The Washington Post]]''\n* [http://www.legistorm.com/member/505/Rep_Mike_Thompson.html Staff salaries, trips and personal finance] at LegiStorm.com\n* [http://www.ontheissues.org/CA/Mike_Thompson.htm Issue positions and quotes] at [[On the Issues]]\n* [http://www.worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n94-76238 Works by or about Mike Thompson] in libraries ([[WorldCat]] catalog)\n* [http://www.c-spanvideo.org/person/57872 Appearances] on [[C-SPAN]] programs\n* [https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/gIQAxsgIAP_topic.html Collected news and commentary] at ''[[The Washington Post]]''\n* -->\n\n{{S-start}}\n{{s-par|us-ca-sen}}\n{{succession box |title=[[California State Senator]], 2nd District |before=[[Barry Keene]] |after=[[Wesley Chesbro]] |years=1990\u20131998}}\n{{s-par|us-hs}}\n{{USRepSuccessionBox\n|state=California\n|district=1\n|before=[[Frank Riggs]]\n|after=[[Doug LaMalfa]]\n|years=1999-2013}}\n{{USRepSuccessionBox\n|state=California\n|district=5\n|before=[[Doris Matsui]]\n|start=2013}}\n{{s-prec|usa}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Mike Simpson]]<br>R-[[Idaho]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=''[[List of current members of the United States House of Representatives by seniority|United States Representatives by seniority]]''|years=81st}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Greg Walden]]<br>R-[[Oregon]]}}\n{{S-end}}\n\n{{CA-FedRep}}\n{{USHouseCurrent}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Thompson, Mike}}\n[[Category:1951 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:American people of English descent]]\n[[Category:American people of Italian descent]]\n[[Category:American people of Swiss descent]]\n[[Category:Members of the United States House of Representatives from California]]\n[[Category:California state senators]]\n[[Category:California Democrats]]\n[[Category:United States Army soldiers]]\n[[Category:California State University, Chico alumni]]\n[[Category:American military personnel of the Vietnam War]]\n[[Category:San Francisco State University faculty]]\n[[Category:California State University, Chico faculty]]\n[[Category:Democratic Party members of the United States House of Representatives]]\n[[Category:People from St. Helena, California]]\n[[Category:21st-century American politicians]]"}]}}}}